MAC OUI vendor data
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The file internal/oui/mac-vendors.txt contains MAC OUI vendor assignments
derived from the IEEE MA-L (MAC Address Block Large) public registry:

    https://standards-oui.ieee.org/oui/oui.txt
    https://standards.ieee.org/products-services/regauth/

The IEEE publishes the MA-L registry as a freely-downloadable public
registry. The vendor-to-OUI assignments are factual data redistributed
here as a lookup table. See "Regenerating OUI data" in CONTRIBUTING.md
for the refresh procedure.

